{"tid":2413423,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【細田守】龍與雀班公主 特報映像","createTime":"2021-02-18T16:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T15:54:25.000Z","uid":4618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63a63844d19a8d903f354952ebbccc1f3a8f25df","tid":2413423,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/studio_chizu/status/1362175927178776576?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudio_chizu%2Fstatus%2F1362175927178776576%3Fs%3D21&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69DKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=7bc7ecbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudio_chizu%2Fstatus%2F1362175927178776576%3Fs%3D21&h=c5b5e9ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/studio_chizu/status/1362175927178776576?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/studio_chizu/status/1362175131225710593?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudio_chizu%2Fstatus%2F1362175131225710593%3Fs%3D21&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69DKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=c19540f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudio_chizu%2Fstatus%2F1362175131225710593%3Fs%3D21&h=4fbbf8dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/studio_chizu/status/1362175131225710593?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ryu-to-sobakasu-no-hime.jp/news/20210218-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fryu-to-sobakasu-no-hime.jp%2Fnews%2F20210218-1.html&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69DKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=000b7e38\" target=\"_blank\">https://ryu-to-sobakasu-no-hime.jp/news/20210218-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n細田守新作留言：<br />\n<br />\n本作《龍與雀斑公主》是「我一直想做的電影」。<br />\n成為動畫電影導演之前我就想著有一天能做出這玩意就好了，也因為至今做出了各種各樣的作品這次才能將其實現。包含戀愛、動作、懸疑要素，另一方面也有生與死這樣本質性的宏大主題，我認為能成為娛樂要素高的電影。<br />\n<br />\n我從前也創作過以網絡世界為題材的電影，想著年輕人會不會把世界變革得有趣又愉快。網絡一方面有著誹謗中傷和假新聞等的負面，但也是能拓展人類可能性的優秀的道具。現在網絡本身也已經改變了，我希望能做出通向積極的未來的電影。<br />\n<br />\n本以為網絡的普及還需要花很多時間，但去年以來工作和生活通過這網絡同常識一起發生了巨大變化，感覺一下子跨到了10年後的未來。不被現在的常識束縛，時代不斷變化，而做出世界變化的電影，是有某種必然性的。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，最終必須要重視的東西肯定是不會變的吧。<br />\n我們世世代代繼承下來的東西，就算世界變化，工具和常識變化，也是會繼承下去的。<br />\n如今這個時代這點就變得更清楚了吧。<br />\n<br />\n世界迅速地變化著，對我們來說真正重要的不變的東西，<br />\n希望能在本作中感受這點。<br />\n<br />\n細田守"},{"pid":"eb2f5e3fe06e340c86422f4bb126dacc0e376dda","tid":2413423,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"唔玩親惰嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58845750e13aa08469778cba30ad5a6c843a9219","tid":2413423,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔玩親情嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ee95057c54ca3e088053d77cb87d1999b04cfc6a","tid":2413423,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee8f61726a0084f5817f7443ed72ed971c77d44","tid":2413423,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58845750e13aa08469778cba30ad5a6c843a9219","tid":2413423,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T16:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔玩親情嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"母と一緒に歌うことが何よりも大好きだったすずは<br />\nその死をきっかけに歌うことができなくなっていた。<br />\n<br />\nいつの間にか父との関係にも溝が生まれ<br />\n現実の世界に心を閉ざすようになっていく。<br />\n<br />\n應該都會有一定分量"}]}